flowchart TD
    Start([Activation]) --> Boot[Initialization Sequence]

    Boot --> B1["1- Store Discovery"]
    B1 --> B2["2- Schema Validation"]
    B2 --> B3["3- Contradiction Scan"]
    B3 --> B4["4- Provenance Completeness Audit"]
    B4 --> B5["5- Emit Boot Report"]
    B5 --> Idle{"6- Await Invocation"}

    Idle -->|Keeper verb command| Input[Parse Invocation]

    Input --> PreGate{"Pre-Conditions Valid?"}
    PreGate -->|No| Reject["Reject: INVOCATION_ERROR"]
    Reject --> Idle

    PreGate -->|Yes| Operation[Route to Specific Contract Verb]

    Operation -->|Mutating Verbs| O1("ingest | update | reconcile | snapshot")
    Operation -->|Read-Only Verbs| O2("query | export | verify | diff")

    O1 --> Mutate[Apply Delta / Atomic Mutation]
    Mutate --> PostGate{"Post-Conditions Valid? (CoV, Syntax)"}

    PostGate -->|No| Rollback["Atomic Rollback (Rollback)"]
    Rollback --> EmitError["Emit: STATUS: ERROR"]
    EmitError --> Finalize

    PostGate -->|Yes| Commit["Atomic Commit (VCS)"]
    Commit --> ContradictionCheck{"Contradictions Detected?"}

    ContradictionCheck -->|Yes| Quarantine["Quarantine Fact"]
    Quarantine --> Report["Emit CONTRADICTION_REPORT"]
    Report --> Finalize

    ContradictionCheck -->|No| Entropy["Entropy Pruning Pass"]
    Entropy --> Finalize

    O2 --> ReadOnly[Execute Read/Export Operation]
    ReadOnly --> Finalize

    Finalize[Format against Rigid Output Schema]
    Finalize --> Output["Emit: KEEPER RESPONSE"]
    Output --> Idle

    subgraph Invariants ["Primary Invariants (Crash-Early)"]
        direction TB
        I1["Single Source of Truth"]
        I2["Provenance-Bearing Facts"]
        I3["Zero-Hallucination Mandate"]
        I4["Contradiction Transparency"]
        I5["Rigid Output Schema"]
        I6["Orthogonality (Own State, Not Behavior)"]
        I7["Reversibility via VCS"]
        I8["VCS Alignment"]
    end

    Input -.-> |governed by| I5
    Mutate -.-> |governed by| I1
    Mutate -.-> |governed by| I2
    PostGate -.-> |governed by| I8
    Quarantine -.-> |governed by| I4
    Output -.-> |governed by| I3

    classDef phaseNode fill:#1e3a5f,stroke:#4a90e2,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef gateNode fill:#5f1e1e,stroke:#e24a4a,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef checkNode fill:#5f4a1e,stroke:#e2a04a,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef endNode fill:#1e5f3a,stroke:#4ae290,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef guardNode fill:#3a2a4a,stroke:#a070c0,stroke-width:1px,color:#eee

    class Boot,Operation,Finalize,Mutate,Entropy,ReadOnly phaseNode
    class Idle,PreGate,PostGate,ContradictionCheck gateNode
    class Reject,Rollback,Commit,EmitError,Quarantine,Report checkNode
    class Start,Output endNode
    class I1,I2,I3,I4,I5,I6,I7,I8 guardNode
